    <script type="text/javascript">
        function getEmbedParameter(url) {
            if (!url) {
                url = window.location.href;
            }
            name = 'embed';
            var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
                results = regex.exec(url);
            if (!results) return null;
            if (!results[2]) return '';
            return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
        }
        function navtosel() {
            var sel = $('#ddRaceType option:selected').val();
            if (sel) {
                var q = '';
                if (sel === '0') q = 'pg=results';
                if (sel === '1') q = 'pg=start';
                if (sel === '2') q = 'pg=register';
                var embed = getEmbedParameter(window.location.href);
                if (typeof embed != "undefined" && embed != null && embed.length > 0) {
                    if (q)
                        q = q + '&embed=' + embed;
                    else
                        q = '?embed=' + embed;
                }
                var newurl = window.location.pathname + "?" + q;
                window.location.assign(newurl);
            }
        }
    </script>
